  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK553">
<l>nāṭoṟu nāṭi muṟaiceyyā maṉṉava </l>
<l>ṉāṭoṟu nāṭu keṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The country of the king who does not daily examine into the wrongs done and distribute justice, will daily fall to ruin.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
